rev 4146:  xela | 2002-12-17 15:19:47 -0500 (Tue, 17 Dec 2002) | 11 lines

Removed unnecessary includes.
Fixed indentation.
Refactored classes.

Overall handling of pools changed. No hierarchival pools
but "global" pools. Lifetime is managed through c++
memory management.
Paths are managed within the Path class.
Apr arrays are replaced by the class Targets.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
