rev 3838:  bmatzelle | 2002-11-20 00:52:08 -0500 (Wed, 20 Nov 2002) | 68 lines


* rapidsvn.dsp
  Added file_action.cpp/.h files.

* src/svncpp/client.cpp (internalPath):
  Updated svn_path_internal_style to match the new API changes.

* src/svn_file_info.cpp (svn_get_file_info):
  Renamed svn_path_split_nts to svn_path_split.

* src/trace_update.cpp (close_file):
  Renamed svn_path_remove_component_nts to svn_path_dirname.

* src/svncpp/modify.cpp (svn_cl__get_log_message):
* src/svncpp/modify.h
  Updated method to include new tmp_file parameter.

* src/rapidsvn_frame.cpp
* src/rapidsvn_frame.h
  (EVT_MENU event table): Moved update and commit to use generic file
  command handler (OnFileCommand).
  (RapidSvnFrame): Add wxCLIP_CHILDREN to both splitter's flags to
  reduce flicker.
  (InitializeMenu): Added new menu items for copying, moving and renaming
  (OnCommit, OnUpdate, MakeUpdate, MakeCommit): Removed these functions,
  moved to OnFileCommand.
  (OnCopyTo, OnMoveTo, OnRenameHere, OnCopyHere): Added these functions,
  empty for now.
  (OnToolLeftClick): Moved update and commit actions to OnFileCommand.
  (GetActionTargets): Moved the code to determine file targets to this
  function so it won't be copied everywhere.
  (OnFileCommand): Moved commit and update to generic file handler.
  (OnFolderBrowserSelChanged): Added stub for code to fix flicker when
  switching tree nodes (not implemented yet).
  (InfoPanel): Changed constructor to add wxCLIP_CHILDREN to reduce
  flicker.

* src/folder_browser.cpp
* src/folder_browser.h
  (FolderBrowser): Changed constructor to add wxCLIP_CHILDREN to reduce
  flicker.
  (OnExpandItem): Add tests for subdirectories in children to ensure
  that the expand boxes are correctly set.
  (hasSubdirectories): Added function to test for subdirectories for a
  particular directory.

* src/file_action.cpp
* src/file_action.h
  Added these files as a copy of action_thread.cpp, action_thread.h.

* src/action_thread.cpp
  (ActionThread, ~ActionThread): Removed the code to set the cursor, as
  this has been move to file_action now.

* src/update_action.cpp
* src/update_action.h
  (Entry, Perform): Refactored these to become PerformUI and Perform to
  work as file_actions.

* src/commit_action.cpp
* src/commit_action.h
  (Entry, Perform): Refactored these to become PerformUI and Perform to
  work as file_actions.

* src/file_list_ctrl.cpp
  (buildMenu): Added menu items to match the items added to the Modify
  menu.

