rev 3462:  bmatzelle | 2002-10-23 13:06:12 -0400 (Wed, 23 Oct 2002) | 24 lines


* src/svncpp/client.cpp
* src/svncpp/client.h
  (status): Switched path input to const char * so that users are not
  forced to include <string> to use the class.
  (singleStatus): New simpler method very similar to the previous method of
  retrieving status for a single file rather than an entire directory.
  Switched the documentation format back to the Doxygen standard.

* src/svncpp/property.cpp
* src/svncpp/property.h
  (beforeFirst): Method for reseting the cursor.
  (propertyValue): Returns the property value of a given key.
  (loadPath): Now gathers the property value from propertyValue().

* src/svncpp/status.cpp (init)
  Now checks if the cmt_author is valid.  New files have no commit author
  so this previously caused a crash.

* src/tests/svncpp/svncpp.cpp
* src/tests/svncpp/svncpp.h
  Changed all methods that use svn::Status to use the new svn::Client 
  singleStatus method instead.

