rev 3403:  bmatzelle | 2002-10-19 16:03:03 -0400 (Sat, 19 Oct 2002) | 30 lines


* src/filelist_ctrl.cpp
* src/filelist_ctrl.h
  (fileStatus): New method that determines what the overall status of a file.
  (UpdateFileList): Uses the fileStatus method to determine the status icon.
  (ShowMenu): Removed references to the Status context menu item.

* src/rapidsvn.rc
  Renamed the mondrian.ico resource to AaLogo so that Windows would use
  it as the binary icon.  It grabs the first alphabetical icon by default.
  Removed the status bitmap reference.

* src/rapidsvn_frame.cpp
* src/rapidsvn_frame.h
  (RapidSvnFrame): Pointed frame icon at AaLogo.
  (ShowStatus, OnStatus): Both are deprecated and thus removed.
  (InitializeMenu): Removed all Status references. 

* src/res/bitmaps/status.bmp
* src/res/bitmaps/status.xpm
  The status dialog functionality is now deprecated so these were removed.

* src/svncpp/log.cpp (formatDate)
  New method to format the output of a Subversion date into a 
  nice human-readable one.

* src/log_dlg.cpp (InitializeList)
  Uses the formatDate() method to make the date human-readable.


