rev 3399:  bmatzelle | 2002-10-18 15:10:52 -0400 (Fri, 18 Oct 2002) | 29 lines


* src/commit_action.cpp (Entry)
  Prints out error messages on commit failure.

* src/filelist_ctrl.cpp (buildMenu)
* src/rapidsvn_frame.cpp (InitializeMenu)
  Renamed menu items "Get latest" to "Update and "Check in" to "Commit".

* src/svn_notify.cpp (SvnNotify)
  Made suppress_final_line false so that it prints out the revision information
  after an event such as an update.

* src/svncpp/auth.h
  (Auth::isAuthenticatied): Returns true if the user successfully authenticated
  with the repository server.
  (prompt): Callback routine for user authentication.
  Added a private variable for authentication failure notification.

* src/svncpp/auth.cpp
  (prompt_user_baton): Baton for the callback authentication module.
  (isAuthenticatied): Returns true if the user successfully authenticated.
  (authenticate): It now sets the auth baton username, password, and
  prompt_baton.  
  (prompt): Callback routine for user authentication.  It doesn't do anything
  but inform the class that the authentication failed.
  
* src/svncpp/log.cpp (loadPath): Removed the un-used baton variable.


