------------------------------------------------------------------------
rev 3288:  xela | 2002-10-04 17:25:32 -0400 (Fri, 04 Oct 2002) | 15 lines

Added new class PatchedGenericDirCtrl as a 
workaround for needed features (workbench) support.

The original dirctrlg.cpp code (wxWindows 2.3.3) has
static method declarations which makes it pretty
impossible to change behaviour by deriving classes.

Hopefully this will be fixed in wxWindows 2.4. Until
then we are using the duplicated code.

* Makefile.in: added object
* patched_dirctrlg.h
* patched_dirctrlg.cpp


------------------------------------------------------------------------
rev 3286:  xela | 2002-10-04 17:18:46 -0400 (Fri, 04 Oct 2002) | 3 lines

