rev 3234:  bmatzelle | 2002-09-26 14:17:15 -0400 (Thu, 26 Sep 2002) | 33 lines


* rapidsvn.cpp (ShowLog):
  Replaced all svn_file_log code with svn::Log.

* rapidsvn.dsp
  Removed svn_file_log.cpp and svn_file_log.h.

* src/svn_file_log.cpp
* src/svn_file_log.h
  Both files are removed because they have been replaced 
  by svn::Log.

* src/svncpp/log.h (loadPath):
  Added some more documentation for effective use of the class.

* src/svncpp/property.cpp
* src/svncpp/property.h
  All of these changes were to make svn::Property behave more 
  like svn::Log.  
  (loadPath): No longer throws an exception.  Now uses vectors 
  to store and retrieve data.
  (isVersioned, first, last, next, previous, reset): All of 
  these methods were added to mirror svn::Log.
  (name): New method returns the current property name.
  (value): New method returns the current property value.

* src/tests/svncpp/svncpp.cpp
  Changed tests to reflect the altered API.

* src/rapidsvn.rc
  Removed delete.wxr reference.


