rev 3223:  jmears | 2002-09-25 16:10:08 -0400 (Wed, 25 Sep 2002) | 19 lines

* update_dlg.cpp
* update_dlg.h
  Reworked the update dialog (UpdateDlg) completely to use sizer
  controls instead of resources, so that it displays well on
  both windows and linux. Data is transferred via a nested data
  structure, using wxValidators. Added a check box for "latest
  revision".
  
* update_action.h
  (UpdateAction): Now stores data in a structure defined by
  UpdateDlg.
  
* update_action.cpp
  (Perform): Simplified the code displaying the dialog.
  (Entry): Now access action data in a structure.

* update.wxr
* update.h
  Deleted, no longer required.
