rev 3207:  bmatzelle | 2002-09-22 22:53:38 -0400 (Sun, 22 Sep 2002) | 37 lines


* src/svncpp/log.cpp
* src/svncpp/log.h
  New class that abstracts the Subversion Log C API.  It works similar
  to JDBC in that it has standard iterators like next() and last ().

* src/preferences_dlg.cpp
* src/preferences_dlg.h
  Added svn:eol-style native.

* src/svncpp/client.cpp
* src/svncpp/client.h
  Moved getRevision() and target() from svn::Modify to this class because it 
  is now used by svn::Log as well.  
  (getRevision): Now it resets the revision template upon each call to the 
  method.  Also, if the revNumber is set to -2 then it defaults to the head 
  of the revision.  

* src/svncpp/modify.cpp
* src/svncpp/modify.h
  Moved getRevision() and target() out of class into svn::Client.

* src/svncpp/status.cpp (textType, propType):
  Fixed crash bug when file is unversioned.

* src/svncpp/svncpp.dsp
  Added svncpp/log.h and svncpp/log.cpp.
  
* src/tests/svncpp/make_repos.bat
* src/tests/svncpp/make_repos.sh
  Added an extra check in for the svn::Log tests.

* src/tests/svncpp/svncpp.cpp
* src/tests/svncpp/svncpp.h
  Added testLog() for testing the svn::Log class.


