* src/svncpp/property.cpp
  Changed parameters from char * to const char *.
  Changed filePath to std::string.

* src/svncpp/status.h
* src/svncpp/status.cpp
  Changed parameters from char * to const char *.
  Changed filePath to std::string.
  loadPath() no longer throws exceptions.  Instead it simply sets 
  versioned to false.

