------------------------------------------------------------------------
rev 3036:  bmatzelle | 2002-08-22 23:27:25 -0400 (Thu, 22 Aug 2002) | 63 lines


The following files encompass the new SvnCpp C++ API.  It is a wrapper library 
over the existing Subversion C API with plenty of data hiding and that good 
C++ feel :)  All classes have been documented in Doxygen format.  All documentation 
is available for viewing and download on the RapidSVN homepage.  All *.h and *.cpp 
files were given the eol-style native propery.

* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/auth.h
* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/auth.cpp
* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/client.h
* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/client.cpp
* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/status.h
* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/status.cpp
* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/property.h
* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/property.cpp
* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/modify.h
* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/modify.cpp
* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/error.h
* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/error.cpp
* rapidsvn/src/svncpp/svncpp.dsp

The following files were added for unit testing with RapidSVN.  Right now 
all of the tests are for the SvnCpp classes.  Read the README.txt for more 
information on using these tests.  All *.h and *.cpp files were given the 
eol-style native propery, as well as README.txt.

* rapidsvn/src/tests/svncpp/svncpptest.dsw
* rapidsvn/src/tests/svncpp/svncpptest.dsp
* rapidsvn/src/tests/svncpp/test_config.ah
* rapidsvn/src/tests/svncpp/README.txt
* rapidsvn/src/tests/svncpp/make_repos.bat
* rapidsvn/src/tests/svncpp/make_repos.sh
* rapidsvn/src/tests/svncpp/main.cpp
* rapidsvn/src/tests/svncpp/svncpp.h
* rapidsvn/src/tests/svncpp/svncpp.cpp

The following header files were modified to incorporate the addition of the 
SvnCpp C++ API.

* rapidsvn/src/commit_action.h
* rapidsvn/src/copy_action.h
* rapidsvn/src/delete_action.h
* rapidsvn/src/import_action.h
* rapidsvn/src/mkdir_action.h

* rapidsvn/src/utils.h (svn_cl_get_log_message):
  This function was removed because it is now re-implemented in the 
  Svn::Modify class.

* rapidsvn/src/utils.cpp
  Same as the header log above.

* rapidsvn/src/delete_action.cpp (Entry):
  This is the first piece of code that uses the SvnCpp code.  

* rapidsvn/rapidsvn.dsw
  Included the svncpp project to the workspace.  It also now has a 
  dependency on the svncpp project.

* rapidsvn/rapidsvn.dsp
  Now includes the svncpp static library.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
rev 2972:  bmatzelle | 2002-08-14 16:15:07 -0400 (Wed, 14 Aug 2002) | 17 lines


* rapidsvn/src/copy_action.cpp (Entry):
  Eliminated 2 un-used variables that were displaying warnings.

* rapidsvn/src/svn_file_status.cpp (retrieveStatus):
  Made function boolean.  Checks if the pool and apr_pool_t is valid.

* rapidsvn/src/svn_file_status.h (retrieveStatus):
  Same as source change above.

* rapidsvn/src/filelist_ctrl.cpp (UpdateFileList):
  If retrieveStatus() fails it displays a load error message rather 
  than continuing.

* rapidsvn/src/rapidsvn.cpp (ShowStatus):
  Skips files in which retrieveStatus() fails.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
rev 2965:  bmatzelle | 2002-08-13 16:23:02 -0400 (Tue, 13 Aug 2002) | 9 lines


* rapidsvn/src/rapidsvn.cpp (OnStatus):
  Removed some code that never was being called.  Removed 
  svn_cl__make_auth_baton() function as it has been replaced 
  by AuthBaton class.

* rapidsvn/TODO.txt
  Added a note on replacing .wxr's with sizers.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
rev 2954:  bmatzelle | 2002-08-12 17:13:47 -0400 (Mon, 12 Aug 2002) | 15 lines


* rapidsvn/src/rapidsvn.rc
  Removed Checkout_Dialog.

* rapidsvn/src/res/bitmaps/folder.ico
* rapidsvn/src/res/bitmaps/versioned_folder.ico
  Reduced images to 256 colors to eliminate first class exception errors.
  Visually cleaned up the image as well.

* rapidsvn/src/copy_action.cpp (Entry):
  Added NULL svn_wc_adm_access_t to implement API change.

* rapidsvn/README.txt
  Fixed autoconf typo.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
rev 2933:  david | 2002-08-10 15:44:05 -0400 (Sat, 10 Aug 2002) | 2 lines

 * packages/rpm/rapidsvn.spec : Added subversion-devel build requirement.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
rev 2932:  bmatzelle | 2002-08-10 14:57:13 -0400 (Sat, 10 Aug 2002) | 21 lines


This commit includes changes to make the RapidSVN GUI 
more cross-platform.

* rapidsvn/src/checkout_action.cpp
  Eliminated resource wxWindows resource loading.

* rapidsvn/src/checkout_dlg.h
  Removed references to the wxWindows resource file.

* rapidsvn/src/checkout_dlg.cpp (InitializeData):
  Removed references to wxWindows resource file and replaced 
  with wxSizer widgets so that GUI controls look the same in
  any GUI environment regardless of size.

* rapidsvn/src/rapidsvn.cpp (BrowseDir):
  Now defaults to the user home directory.

* rapidsvn/src/res/checkout.wxr
  Removed now that it is not needed.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
rev 2906:  bmatzelle | 2002-08-06 23:02:35 -0400 (Tue, 06 Aug 2002) | 8 lines


* rapidsvn/README.txt
  Added information on building with Linux.

* rapidsvn/src/Makefile.in
  Removed copy_dlg.cpp as a build requirement.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
rev 2891:  bmatzelle | 2002-08-06 00:31:37 -0400 (Tue, 06 Aug 2002) | 33 lines


The following files were removed because they were part of the 
now obsolete copy functionality:

* rapidsvn/src/copy_dlg.cpp
* rapidsvn/src/copy_dlg.h
* rapidsvn/src/res/copy.h
* rapidsvn/src/res/copy.wxr

* rapidsvn/src/copy_action.cpp (Entry, DestinationPath):
  Added DestinationPath and Entry code for supporting the Subversion 
  copy action.  Now it uses a directory dialog to copy on the local
  machine rather than on the remote repository.

* rapidsvn/src/copy_action.h
  Added the DestinationPath prototype and removed a bunch of 
  un-needed variables.

* rapidsvn/src/rapidsvn.cpp (MakeCopy, Rename):
  Added some functional copy code and a stub for Rename.

* rapidsvn/src/rapidsvn.h
  Added the prototypes for the copy and rename functionalities.

* rapidsvn/src/rapidsvn.rc
  Eliminated the reference to the deprecated Copy_Dialog.

* rapidsvn/rapidsvn.dsp
  Removed the deprecated src/copy_dlg.cpp and src/copy_dlg.h.

* rapidsvn/src/notify.cpp (notify):
  Made the logging more understandable by change 'A' to 'Added', etc.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
