rev 2839:  bmatzelle | 2002-07-31 22:54:20 -0400 (Wed, 31 Jul 2002) | 20 lines


* rapidsvn/src/filelist_ctrl.cpp (UpdateFileList, BuildMenu):
  Now files without extensions (*) will be found in the file list pane.
  'Update' and 'Commit' were renamed to 'Get latest' and 'Check in' 
  respectively on the pop up menu.
  
* rapidsvn/src/rapidsvn.cpp (InitializeMenu):
  'Update' and 'Commit' were renamed to 'Get latest' and 'Check in' 
  respectively on the Modify menu.

* rapidsvn/TODO.txt
  Added a bunch of new TODO items.

* rapidsvn/HACKING.txt
  First draft of a HACKING document for RapidSVN.  Pretty much a condensed 
  copy of Subversion's hacking document with a few changes.

* rapidsvn/LICENSE.txt
  Made the eol-style property native.

